A.)We should have Node n NPM(Node Package Manager) installed, Check the versions on your machine.
    Node - **node --version**
    NPM - **npm --version**
    
B.)Since we will need to continuously change/update code, We want it to Auto-Monitor/Hot-Reload, Install Nodemon.
    **npm install nodemon**
    
C.)Initialize npm using below command.
    **npm init**

D.)Install Express package using below command
    **npm install express --save
